Entries.default: "Never could have guessed we'd make it this far."
"Captain, a moment? I've got a job needs handling."
"High time we got to know each other, captain."
"Never saw myself on the wrong side of history before."
"Wish it could have happened differently, captain."
"I know how this must look. We can talk if you're feeling up to it."
"With everything piling on us at once, seems like a good time to talk in private."
"Pretty sure I've seen everything now, captain."
"All those people. Good soldiers. Can't get it out of my head."
"You... you got any relationship tips, captain?"
